metadata.name: After party
metadata.description:
“After party” by Ken Hamala
Ink on Paper and colouring on Adobe illustrator
Size: 5019 × 2481 / 300 dpi
1/1

We human fear these scary monsters that eat trash like hot charcoal. We do not care about and never love them. But one day when their poops turn out to be something very pricy, the world we know will never be the same.
